description	"B1 'Engineer' Battledroid

^2Weapons:
- Blaster Pistol (2)
- CP-50 Spray-Gun: (2)
- 1 Battledroid Sonic Detonator

^6Equipment:
- Deployable Sentry Gun

^8Attributes:
- Higher Processing Speed [Fast Hacking]
- Shield Recharge (1)
- 2 Reinforcements
- Assemble (1)

^3Abilities:
- Portable Repair Kit [Hold Use on Allies]
- Portable Ammo Distribution Pack [Press Use to Drop Ammo for Allies]
- 6 Tracking Darts ^3[CS2 Melee]

A Battledroid of the Trade Federation, now part of the huge droid army being assembled for the CIS. Easy to take down, but but in groups much more deadly. The Engineer battledroid carries a powerful spraygun, a sentry turret, and a pair of concussion grenades. Most Generally, however, the Engineer serves support purposes, provding other droids with ammunition and repairs."